<p>
  <span class="nym">Bonamice</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>bona</i> 'good' + <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>amica</i> 'friend'.
</span>
  
